## Key Architecture Decisions (Rationale)

| Decision | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|
| Server-authoritative game loop | Prevents cheating; single source of truth for all physics |
| Raw HTML Canvas (no Phaser/Pixi) | Lean bundle, full rendering control, no framework overhead |
| Incremental state diffs each tick | Reduces WebSocket bandwidth vs sending full state |
| UUID cookie identity | Zero-friction player identity, no registration required |
| In-memory room state | Rooms are ephemeral; avoiding DB writes mid-game keeps latency low |
| Shared `packages/shared` | Single source of truth for types/constants prevents client-server drift |
| pnpm workspaces monorepo | Single repo, shared tooling, easy cross-package imports |

